  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

  Data Flow

  1. UserContextBuilder queries Neo4j with MEGA-QUERY (382 lines of Cypher!)
  2. Populates UserContext (~240 fields) with UIDs + optional rich entities
  3. Services declare dependency on Context Awareness Protocols (slices of UserContext)
  4. UserContextIntelligence orchestrates 13 domain services to answer "what should I work on?"

