  4. Separation of Concerns Analysis

  Good Separations

  | Concern         | Location                  | Clean? |
  |-----------------|---------------------------|--------|
  | Domain entities | /core/models/             | ✅      |
  | Protocols       | /core/services/protocols/ | ✅      |
  | Backends        | /adapters/persistence/    | ✅      |
