  Problematic Separations

  | Concern                  | Issue                                                |
  |--------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|
  | Context Building         | Split across 4+ files                                |
  | Intelligence             | Multiple overlapping services                        |
  | Query Generation         | CypherGenerator + UnifiedQueryBuilder + QueryBuilder |
  | Rich vs Standard Context | Two paths with different data shapes                 |

